:: CC-sexPreference [creation-page nobr]
<div id="cc-sexpref-root">
	What role do you normally play as during sex?

	<<set _prefs = setup.sexpreference >>
	<<CCChoiceButtons $mc "sexpref" _prefs "#cc-sexpref-root" "CC-sexPreference">>
	<br>
	<<button "Confirm">>
		<<if !$mc.sexpref>>
			<span class="red">Please choose a sex preference.</span>
		<<else>>
			<<set $pages.sexpref = true>>
			<<goto "Index-CC">>
		<</if>>
	<</button>>
</div>